GITHUB DESKTOP
- create a new repository
    > enter the name of the new repository
    > change the file path (make sure that it is in the htdocs folder of xampp)
    > click publish
    > uncheck the ckeckbox "keep the code private"
    > click publish repository
- click "Open in Visual Studio Code"

VISUAL STUDIO CODE
- Terminal
    > composer create-project laravel/laravel:^9.0 example-app(Laravel-lang-to)
    > git add .
    > git status
    > git commit -m "New comment"
    > git push origin HEAD
